platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Khan Academy Kids teaches early literacy, language, math, and social and emotional skills throughout its more than 1,000 games, videos, and stories. The app integrates science lessons from National Geographic Young Explorer magazine, music from Super Simple Songs, and content from childrens nonfiction publisher Bellwether Media.

With content from big names like National Geographic, this app teaches early literacy, language and maths, as well and social and emotional skills, throughout its more than 1,000 games, videos and stories.
